            Et si cultiver l’effervescence de votre mission faisait toute la différence ?
        </h1>
        <div class="col-span-4 col-start-9 pt-fluid-4xl pr-fluid-sixty pb-fluid-4xl">
            <Icon name="plant" class="h-auto w-full mix-blend-multiply" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="mob-version grid grid-cols-8 items-center justify-center gap-mob-16 bg-yellow pt-mob-64 pr-mob-16 pb-mob-64 pl-mob-16"
    >
        <div class="col-span-6 col-start-2 flex flex-col gap-mob-64">
            <Icon name="plant" class="h-auto w-full mix-blend-multiply" />
            <h1
                class="font-radio flex flex-col justify-center text-mob-md leading-[105%] font-normal tracking-[0%]"
            >
                Et si cultiver l’effervescence de votre mission faisait toute la différence ?
            </h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="desktop-version flex h-fit flex-col bg-offwhite pt-fluid-forty pr-fluid-forty pb-fluid-eighty pl-fluid-forty"
    >
        <div
            class="font-radio flex w-full flex-row items-center justify-center border-b border-b-perle pb-3 text-body-sm tracking-[3%] uppercase"
        >
            Nos programmes
        </div>
        <div
            class="relative grid grid-cols-12 gap-fluid-twenty bg-offwhite pt-fluid-forty pr-fluid-forty pl-fluid-forty"
